data.description: Gorgeous property set back off Poodle Creek Rd. on Long Tom River.  Certified organic nursery for 10 years. Greenhouses,  irrigation set up, solid wood frame barn with stalls and implement storage barn.  Open pastures, fruit trees, extensive established raspberry crop  southern exposure, fenced, views of distant hills. Cozy bungalow/farmhouse with 15x32 great space above newer garage building. Detached additional living space with large bedroom, bath and at one time a space for a kitchenette, covered carport.  Wonderful opportunity! Turn key farming operation with established raspberries, strawberries and history of vegetables, other berries, small apple orchard. If  you want or just a nice country property with very usable land for horses, cattle?  Or just enjoying!   4.8 acres of water rights to Long Tom river..AT THIS PRICE THE PROPAGATION GREENHOUSE, PERMANENT GREENHOUSE AND COOLER ARE INCLUDED. SOME ADDITIONAL IMPLEMENTS, TRACTOR, IRRIGATION COMPONENTS AVAILABLE UPON NEGOTIATION.
